OL,6,FA North East university has warned job
OL,7,Flosses could be on the way as it tries
OL,8,Fto cut costs.
OL,10,FStaff at were told on Monday 12
OL,11,FFebruary that the budget for staffing
OL,12,Ffaces being cut by #12.5m.
OL,14,FThe university is one of major
OL,15,Femployers, with around 3,000 staff.
