OL,3,CUniversity job loss warning as staff
OL,4,Cbudget faces #12.5m cut
OL,6,FIn an email, vice-chancellor and chief
OL,7,Fexecutive Professor Andy Long wrote
OL,8,Fthat savings are needed "in order to
OL,9,Fensure we are able to cover our
OL,10,Fcosts", but pledged to do "all that we
OL,11,Fcan" to avoid compulsory redundancies.
OL,13,FHe blamed a "volatile" market for
OL,14,Frecruiting students from overseas and
OL,15,Fthe Government making it "more
OL,16,Fdifficult" to do so, saying the
OL,17,Funiversity's income was projected to
OL,18,Fbe #10 million lower in the next
OL,19,Facademic year as a result, as well as
OL,20,Fpressures caused by inflation.
