OL,4,Cbudget faces #12.5m cut
OL,6,F"This is a consequence of a
OL,7,Fcombination of fixed home
OL,8,Fundergraduate fees, difficulties
OL,9,Faround recruitment of international
OL,10,Fstudents, and the ongoing impact of
OL,11,Finflation.
OL,13,F"To remain competitive and to create
OL,14,Froom for investment in our future
OL,15,Fstrategic plans, the university must
OL,16,Faddress its cost base through changes
OL,17,Fto staff and non-staff budgets.
