OL,6,F"In doing so we will ensure we protect
OL,7,Fthe student experience while
OL,8,Fsupporting our staff through this
OL,9,Fchallenging period. We will do all
OL,10,Fthat we can to avoid compulsory
OL,11,Fredundancies while we go through this
OL,12,Fprocess."
OL,14,FIn his email, Prof Long said that #16m
OL,15,Fworth of savings had already been made
OL,16,Fthis year and a further #4m of
OL,17,Fspending reductions already identified
OL,18,Fin non-staffing areas.
