OL,6,FHowever, he added that the "working
OL,7,Fassumption is that we now need to
OL,8,Freduce our current staff costs by a
OL,9,Ffurther #12.5m from an overall budget
OL,10,Fof #225m".
OL,12,FThe vice chancellor said that
OL,13,FNorthumbria University would seek to
OL,14,Fincrease its recruitment of home
OL,15,Fstudents to around 6,000 per year,
OL,16,Ffrom a current 5,400, because of
OL,17,Fconcerns about the international
OL,18,Fstudent market.
