OL,6,FHe told staff that the university will
OL,7,Fhave approximately 700 fewer students
OL,8,Fon its Newcastle campus in 2024/25
OL,9,Fthan it had five years earlier, while
OL,10,Fduring which time its workforce had
OL,11,Fgrown by 500.
OL,13,FProf Long also highlighted higher
OL,14,Fenergy prices and a "further #4m
OL,15,Fstrain on our budgets" from the
OL,16,FTeachers Pension Scheme as factors
OL,17,Fbehind the savings plan.
